  Name: Tommaso, Knight
  Icon: {fileID: 1208347981, guid: b2407ce4cf73ad348aec15ba9990f7a1, type: 3}
  Description: "He thought war was ceremony \u2014 velvet, banners, and feasts. A
    scimitar removed that fantasy and half his arm. Blood pumped in a straight line
    onto stone.\n\nTreatment: Tourniquet high at the shoulder. Saw fast before panic
    destroys will. cauterize if spurting continues. Wrap linen tight.\n\nRequires:
    4 Bandages"
